title: Minecraft: Story Mode Episode 1-3-GOG

Minecraft: Story Mode - Episode 1-3 (c) Telltale Games

Release Date : 11/2015
Protection : -
Discs : 1
Genre : Adventure
Languages : EN/FR/DE/ES/PT/CN-S/RU

THE ADVENTURE OF A LIFETIME IN THE WORLD OF MINECRAFT In this five
part episodic series, youll embark on a perilous adventure across
the Overworld, through the Nether, to the End, and beyond. You and
your friends revere the legendary Order of the Stone: Warrior,
Redstone Engineer, Griefer, and Architect; slayers of the Ender
Dragon. While at EnderCon in hopes of meeting Gabriel the Warrior,
you and your friends discover that something is wrong something
dreadful.

For more info go to : http://www.gog.com/game/minecraft_story_mode
